# Security Rules

- PIN hashing: SHA-256 using the crypto package
- Never log PINs, even hashed ones
- Locked apps list stored in SharedPreferences must be encrypted
- Profile data in sqflite must never include raw PINs
- Auth should support both PIN and Biometric (BiometricPrompt)
- Each profile can only be edited after entering that profile's own PIN
